---
layout: base.njk
title: "Digitizing Factory Operations"
description: "Led end-to-end digital transformation of a packaged drinking water factory by designing and implementing a web & mobile-based tracking system."
permalink: /work/factory-project/digitizing-factory-operations/
---

<style>
  .fp-wrap { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem; }

  /* ── Process phase strip ─────────────────────────────── */
  .phase-strip {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(8, 1fr);
    gap: 0;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .phase-item {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
    padding: 1.25rem 0.5rem;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-align: center; position: relative;
    background: var(--surface);
  }
  .phase-item:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .phase-item::after {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute; right: -8px; top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    color: var(--fire); font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .phase-item:last-child::after { display: none; }
  .phase-circle {
    width: 64px; height: 64px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--lifted); border: 2px solid var(--border2);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
  }
  .phase-item:hover .phase-circle {
    border-color: var(--fire); background: rgba(255,77,28,0.08);
  }
  .phase-name {
    font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--fire);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem; line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .phase-desc {
    font-size: 0.58rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* ── Role icon grid ──────────────────────────────────── */
  .role-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
    gap: 1px; background: var(--border);
  }
  .role-item {
    background: var(--surface); padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem; text-align: center;
  }
  .role-icon {
    width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--lifted); border: 1px solid var(--border2);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
  }
  .role-label {
    font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--sub); line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* ── Stat cards ──────────────────────────────────────── */
  .stat-row {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1px; background: var(--border);
  }
  .stat-box {
    background: var(--deep); padding: 1.5rem;
  }
  .stat-num {
    font-family: var(--serif); font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 2rem; color: var(--fire); line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }
  .stat-title {
    font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--bright);
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }
  .stat-sub { font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--muted); }

  /* ── Before/After ────────────────────────────────────── */
  .ba-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1px; background: var(--border);
  }
  .ba-col { padding: 2rem; }
  .ba-row {
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.65rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-size: 0.83rem; line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .ba-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .ba-dot {
    width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.4rem;
  }

  /* ── Dashboard mockup ────────────────────────────────── */
  .browser-bar {
    background: var(--lifted); padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .b-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; }

  /* ── Section divider with label ──────────────────────── */
  .sec-divider {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .sec-divider::before {
    content: ''; display: block; width: 28px; height: 2px;
    background: var(--fire); flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ── Learning cards ──────────────────────────────────── */
  .learn-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 1rem;
  }
  .learn-card {
    background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--fire); padding: 1.5rem;
  }
  .learn-card h4 {
    font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--fire); margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }
  .learn-card p { font-size: 0.83rem; color: var(--sub); line-height: 1.7; margin:0; }
</style>

<!-- ── HERO ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section style="background:var(--deep); border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); padding:5rem 2rem 4rem; position:relative; overflow:hidden;">
  <div aria-hidden="true" style="position:absolute;top:-20%;right:0;width:600px;height:600px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(255,77,28,0.07) 0%,transparent 65%);pointer-events:none;"></div>
  <div class="fp-wrap">
    <div class="label fu" style="display:flex;gap:0.6rem;margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
      <a href="/work/" style="color:var(--muted);" onmouseover="this.style.color='var(--bright)'" onmouseout="this.style.color='var(--muted)'">Work</a>
      <span style="color:var(--border2);">/</span>
      <span style="color:var(--sub);">Factory Project</span>
    </div>

    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:5rem;align-items:end;">
      <div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:0.5rem;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:1.5rem;" class="fu">
          <span class="badge">Freelance</span>
          <span class="badge" style="background:var(--lifted);color:var(--sub);border:1px solid var(--border2);">Uzbekistan</span>
          <span class="badge" style="background:var(--lifted);color:var(--sub);border:1px solid var(--border2);">2024</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="display fu fu1" style="font-size:clamp(2.4rem,5vw,4rem);margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
          Digitizing Factory<br />Operations: <em>From<br />Paper to Real-Time</em>
        </h1>
        <p class="fu fu2" style="color:var(--sub);line-height:1.85;max-width:40ch;font-size:0.92rem;">
          Led end-to-end digital transformation of a packaged drinking water factory in Uzbekistan — designing and implementing a web &amp; mobile production tracking system.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="fu fu3">
        <table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;">
          <tr style="border-top:1px solid var(--border);">
            <td class="label" style="padding:1rem 0;width:42%;">My Role</td>
            <td style="padding:1rem 0;color:var(--bright);font-weight:600;font-size:0.85rem;">Project Manager &amp; Design Lead</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-top:1px solid var(--border);">
            <td class="label" style="padding:1rem 0;">Industry</td>
            <td style="padding:1rem 0;color:var(--bright);font-weight:600;font-size:0.85rem;">Packaged Drinking Water Factory</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-top:1px solid var(--border);">
            <td class="label" style="padding:1rem 0;">Deliverables</td>
            <td style="padding:1rem 0;color:var(--bright);font-weight:600;font-size:0.85rem;line-height:1.8;">Web Dashboard · Mobile App · System Architecture</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-top:1px solid var(--border);">
            <td class="label" style="padding:1rem 0;">Team</td>
            <td style="padding:1rem 0;color:var(--bright);font-weight:600;font-size:0.85rem;">2–4 Freelance Developers</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);"><td colspan="2" style="padding:0;"></td></tr>
        </table>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:0.4rem;margin-top:1.25rem;">
          {% for c in ["Project Management","System Design","Team Leadership","Web + Mobile","Digital Transformation"] %}
          <span style="font-size:0.58rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:3px 9px;background:var(--lifted);border:1px solid var(--border2);color:var(--sub);">{{ c }}</span>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── OUTCOME STATS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<div style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">
  <div class="fp-wrap" style="padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0;">
    <div class="stat-row">
      {% for s in [["⚡","~70%","Faster reporting","vs daily paper logs"],["🔍","100%","Live visibility","Zero blind spots"],["📦","Real-time","Inventory tracking","Automated logging"],["🧾","10×","Easier audits","Full digital trail"]] %}
      <div class="stat-box">
        <div style="font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:0.3rem;">{{ s[0] }}</div>
        <div class="stat-num">{{ s[1] }}</div>
        <div class="stat-title">{{ s[2] }}</div>
        <div class="stat-sub">{{ s[3] }}</div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ── PROCESS FLOW ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section style="padding:5rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--deep);">
  <div class="fp-wrap">
    <div class="sec-divider">
      <span class="label">The Process</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="display" style="font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);margin-bottom:0.75rem;">
      Packaged Drinking Water Plant <em>Digitization</em>
    </h2>
    <p style="color:var(--sub);margin-bottom:2.5rem;font-size:0.88rem;">Digitizing Production &amp; Inventory System in Uzbekistan</p>

    <!-- Phase strip — matches Canva horizontal flow -->
    <div class="phase-strip">
      {% set phases = [
        ["📋","Problem Identification","Manual data collection & pain mapping"],
        ["🗺️","Workflow Planning","Process mapping & strategy"],
        ["🎨","UI Prototyping","App design & mockups"],
        ["👨‍💻","Development Coordination","Working with developers"],
        ["🔍","Testing & QA","Bug testing & fixes"],
        ["👥","Staff Training","Employee instruction"],
        ["🚀","System Launch","Digital implementation"],
        ["📊","Results & Benefits","Live reporting & transparency"]
      ] %}
      {% for p in phases %}
      <div class="phase-item">
        <div class="phase-circle">{{ p[0] }}</div>
        <div class="phase-name">{{ p[1] }}</div>
        <div class="phase-desc">{{ p[2] }}</div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    <!-- Bridge statement -->
    <div style="margin-top:2rem;background:var(--fire);padding:1.5rem 2rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1.5rem;">
      <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" style="flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
      <p style="font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;color:#fff;line-height:1.4;letter-spacing:-0.01em;margin:0;">
        "From Manual Logs to Digital Efficiency"
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── MY ROLE & CONTRIBUTIONS ───────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section style="padding:5rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">
  <div class="fp-wrap">
    <div class="sec-divider">
      <span class="label">My Role &amp; Contributions</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="display" style="font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
      Project Manager — <em>Design &amp; Delivery Lead</em>
    </h2>

    <div class="role-grid" style="margin-bottom:2rem;">
      {% set roles = [
        ["✏️","Product Design","Designed all UI screens for web and mobile"],
        ["⚙️","Project Coordination","Managed team, timeline and delivery"],
        ["✅","QA Testing","Tested all features in real factory conditions"],
        ["👨‍🏫","Staff Training","Trained factory workers to use the system"],
        ["📈","Reporting","Built reporting dashboards for management"]
      ] %}
      {% for r in roles %}
      <div class="role-item">
        <div class="role-icon">{{ r[0] }}</div>
        <div class="role-label">{{ r[1] }}</div>
        <p style="font-size:0.68rem;color:var(--muted);margin:0;line-height:1.5;">{{ r[2] }}</p>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    <!-- Highlight card -->
    <div style="background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);padding:1.75rem 2rem;border-left:3px solid var(--fire);">
      <p style="font-family:var(--serif);font-style:italic;font-size:1.2rem;color:var(--bright);line-height:1.45;margin:0;letter-spacing:-0.01em;">
        "Bridged factory operations with a freelance tech team to deliver a working digital system — on time, on budget, and actually used by workers on the floor."
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── PROBLEM: BEFORE vs AFTER ──────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section style="padding:5rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--deep);">
  <div class="fp-wrap">
    <div class="sec-divider">
      <span class="label">The Problem</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="display" style="font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
      A factory running blind <em>on pen &amp; paper.</em>
    </h2>

    <div class="ba-grid">
      <div class="ba-col" style="background:var(--surface);">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.6rem;margin-bottom:1rem;">
          <span style="width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--muted);display:inline-block;"></span>
          <span class="label">Before</span>
        </div>
        {% for item in ["Workers fill paper logbooks every shift","Supervisor collects sheets manually","Someone tallies numbers in a spreadsheet","Printed monthly reports — often wrong","Auditors request physical paper binders","No visibility into live production status"] %}
        <div class="ba-row" style="color:var(--sub);">
          <span class="ba-dot" style="background:var(--muted);"></span>{{ item }}
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      <div class="ba-col" style="background:var(--lifted);">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.6rem;margin-bottom:1rem;">
          <span style="width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--fire);display:inline-block;"></span>
          <span class="label" style="color:var(--fire);">After</span>
        </div>
        {% for item in ["Workers tap entries on a mobile app","Data syncs to the server instantly","Dashboard auto-calculates all totals","Live charts update in real time","One-click export for any audit period","Managers see everything from anywhere"] %}
        <div class="ba-row" style="color:var(--text);">
          <span class="ba-dot" style="background:var(--fire);"></span>{{ item }}
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── DASHBOARD SCREENSHOT / MOCKUP ─────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section style="padding:5rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">
  <div class="fp-wrap">
    <div class="sec-divider">
      <span class="label">The System</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="display" style="font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
      Web dashboard + <em>mobile app.</em>
    </h2>

    <!-- Browser mockup with dashboard representation -->
    <div style="background:var(--deep);border:1px solid var(--border);overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:1rem;">
      <div class="browser-bar">
        <div class="b-dot" style="background:#ff5f57;"></div>
        <div class="b-dot" style="background:#febc2e;"></div>
        <div class="b-dot" style="background:#28c840;"></div>
        <div style="flex:1;background:var(--border);height:20px;margin-left:0.75rem;border-radius:3px;display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 0.75rem;">
          <span style="font-size:0.6rem;color:var(--muted);">factory-system.uz/dashboard</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Dashboard layout representation -->
      <div style="padding:1.5rem;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:8px;margin-bottom:8px;">
        {% for label in ["Bottles Today","Active Machines","Shift Output","Inventory Level"] %}
        <div style="background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);padding:1rem;text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-size:0.55rem;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:0.4rem;">{{ label }}</div>
          <div style="font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:900;font-size:1.4rem;color:var(--fire);">—</div>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      <div style="padding:0 1.5rem 1.5rem;display:grid;grid-template-columns:2fr 1fr;gap:8px;">
        <div style="background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);height:140px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-direction:column;gap:0.5rem;">
          <!-- Fake chart bars -->
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-end;gap:4px;height:80px;">
            {% for h in [40,65,50,80,55,90,70,85,60,75] %}
            <div style="width:18px;background:var(--fire);opacity:0.7;border-radius:1px 1px 0 0;" :style="height:{{ h }}px"></div>
            {% endfor %}
            <div style="width:18px;height:40px;background:var(--fire);opacity:0.3;border-radius:1px 1px 0 0;"></div>
            <div style="width:18px;height:65px;background:var(--fire);opacity:0.3;border-radius:1px 1px 0 0;"></div>
            <div style="width:18px;height:50px;background:var(--fire);opacity:0.3;border-radius:1px 1px 0 0;"></div>
            <div style="width:18px;height:80px;background:var(--fire);opacity:0.8;border-radius:1px 1px 0 0;"></div>
            <div style="width:18px;height:55px;background:var(--fire);opacity:0.6;border-radius:1px 1px 0 0;"></div>
            <div style="width:18px;height:90px;background:var(--fire);opacity:0.9;border-radius:1px 1px 0 0;"></div>
          </div>
          <span class="label" style="color:var(--border2);">Daily production chart</span>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;">
          <div style="background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);flex:1;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;">
            <span class="label" style="color:var(--border2);">Inventory status</span>
          </div>
          <div style="background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);flex:1;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;">
            <span class="label" style="color:var(--border2);">Recent logs</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Mobile + web split feature list -->
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1px;background:var(--border);">
      <div style="background:var(--surface);padding:1.75rem;">
        <p class="label" style="color:var(--fire);margin-bottom:1.25rem;">🌐 Web System — Manager Dashboard</p>
        {% for f in ["Live production tracking per shift","Inventory overview — in &amp; out","One-click report export","Anomaly alerts when output drops"] %}
        <div style="display:flex;gap:0.75rem;align-items:flex-start;padding:0.7rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--sub);">
          <span style="color:var(--fire);flex-shrink:0;">→</span>{{ f }}
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--surface);padding:1.75rem;">
        <p class="label" style="color:var(--fire);margin-bottom:1.25rem;">📱 Mobile App — Worker Interface</p>
        {% for f in ["4-tap data entry form","Works offline — syncs when connected","Simple worker ID login (no email needed)","Uzbek &amp; Russian language support"] %}
        <div style="display:flex;gap:0.75rem;align-items:flex-start;padding:0.7rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--sub);">
          <span style="color:var(--fire);flex-shrink:0;">→</span>{{ f }}
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── TEAM STRUCTURE ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section style="padding:5rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--deep);">
  <div class="fp-wrap">
    <div class="sec-divider">
      <span class="label">Team Structure</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="display" style="font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
      Leader, <em>not just executor.</em>
    </h2>

    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:3rem;align-items:start;">
      <!-- Org chart -->
      <div style="background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);padding:2.5rem;text-align:center;">
        <div style="display:inline-flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:0;width:100%;">
          <div style="background:var(--fire);padding:0.75rem 2rem;font-weight:700;font-size:0.82rem;letter-spacing:0.05em;color:#fff;display:inline-block;">YOU — Project Manager</div>
          <div style="width:1px;height:24px;background:var(--border2);"></div>
          <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:1px;background:var(--border2);width:100%;">
            {% for d in ["Dev 1","Dev 2","Dev 3"] %}
            <div style="background:var(--lifted);padding:0.6rem 0.5rem;font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--sub);text-align:center;">Freelance {{ d }}</div>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
          <div style="width:1px;height:24px;background:var(--border2);"></div>
          <div style="background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border2);padding:0.6rem 2rem;font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--muted);display:inline-block;width:100%;">Factory Staff — End Users</div>
        </div>
        <p style="margin-top:1.5rem;font-size:0.72rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;max-width:28ch;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;">
          Managed a small freelance team — translating factory operations into technical execution.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- What this meant in practice -->
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;">
        {% for item in [
          ["📝","Wrote specs clear enough for remote devs to execute without daily calls"],
          ["🤝","Resolved conflicts between factory manager expectations and technical constraints"],
          ["💰","Kept the project on budget despite mid-project scope changes"],
          ["🏭","Earned trust on the factory floor to drive real adoption"],
          ["📦","Delivered a working system — not just a prototype"]
        ] %}
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:1rem;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);padding:1rem 1.25rem;">
          <span style="font-size:1rem;flex-shrink:0;">{{ item[0] }}</span>
          <span style="font-size:0.83rem;color:var(--sub);line-height:1.6;">{{ item[1] }}</span>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── KEY LEARNINGS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section style="padding:5rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">
  <div class="fp-wrap">
    <div class="sec-divider">
      <span class="label">Key Learnings</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="display" style="font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
      What this project <em>taught me.</em>
    </h2>
    <div class="learn-grid">
      {% for l in [
        ["🏭","Usability in industrial environments","Simple is not obvious. Designing for non-technical users in a physically demanding environment forced me to strip every screen to its absolute minimum."],
        ["🤝","Managing non-technical stakeholders","Factory managers think in outcomes, not features. Framing every decision as a business result — not a technical one — was the real skill."],
        ["🌐","Coordinating remote freelance teams","Clear written specs, recorded decisions, and short feedback loops matter more than talent. Structure is what makes remote work actually work."]
      ] %}
      <div class="learn-card">
        <div style="font-size:1.4rem;margin-bottom:0.6rem;">{{ l[0] }}</div>
        <h4>{{ l[1] }}</h4>
        <p>{{ l[2] }}</p>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

